Roles:
Ambassador: Out of cards in the court and your own, choose to keep 2

Assassin: Pay 3 coins to the Treasury and launch an assassination against another player. If successful that player immediately loses a card.

Captian: Take 2 coins from another player. If they only have one coin, take only one. (Can be blocked by the Ambassador or the Captain)

Contessa: Can block assassination

Duke: Take 3 coins from the Treasury. Can block foreign aid

All roles can claim foreign aid


Class Player: player.h
int coins;
Role[] hand;

Class: Role

